      "text": "SCOOP: Trump's DC Task Force has cleaned out 142 homeless encampments throughout the city + now there are no known encampments between National Park Service units in the D.C. area parks, according to data provided with @DailyCaller. \n\nIt's been one year since the “Make D.C. Safe and Beautiful Task Force” was created. They've made 11,205 arrests of 62 known gang members, 1,956 narcotics subjects, 1,036 subjects of firearms offenses and 30 homicide subjects in the last 365.",
